:: DEMO-100 Arrival
<<silently>>
<<set $header.location to "City Centre">>
<<set $header.time to "Monday, 08:00">>
<<emote-calm>>
<<avatar-setBody "fair">>
<<wear-blackTshirt>>
<<wear-darkJeans>>
<<wear-sneakers>>
<</silently>>
<<header>>
<<page>>

<<first>>
The taxi drops you at the corner of 5th and Main. The city is already alive with morning traffic, horns honking in the distance.
<<then>>
You're back at the corner of 5th and Main. The coffee shop across the street looks inviting.
<<finally>>
5th and Main. You know this corner well now.
<</first>>

You adjust your bag and look around. A tall glass building rises ahead of you &mdash; that must be the office.

<<addNotification "You have arrived at City Centre.">>

[[Enter the building|DEMO-200 Lobby]]
[[Explore the street|DEMO-300 Street]]
<</page>>


:: DEMO-200 Lobby
<<silently>>
<<set $header.location to "Office Building &mdash; Lobby">>
<<set $header.time to "Monday, 08:15">>
<<emote-smile>>
<</silently>>
<<header>>
<<page>>

The lobby is all marble and chrome. A security guard behind the front desk looks up as you enter.

<div class="dialogue">
    <span class="speaker">Guard:</span> "Good morning. <<playerName>>, right? <<playerFaction>> sent word you'd be arriving. Take the elevator to the third floor."
</div>

<<emote-surprised>>

//How does he know your name already?//

<<rollDice "1d6">>
<<if _diceResult gte 4>>
    Your training kicks in. You keep your expression neutral and nod.
    <<addNotification "Composure check: passed (rolled _diceResult)">>
<<else>>
    You can't quite hide your surprise. The guard smirks.
    <<addNotification "Composure check: failed (rolled _diceResult)">>
<</if>>
<</rollDice>>

[[Take the elevator|DEMO-400 Office]]
[[Ask how he knows your name|DEMO-210 Question]]
<</page>>


:: DEMO-210 Question
<<silently>>
<<emote-frown>>
<</silently>>
<<header>>
<<page>>

<div class="dialogue">
    <span class="speaker"><<playerName>>:</span> "How do you know who I am?"
</div>

The guard taps a folder on his desk.

<div class="dialogue">
    <span class="speaker">Guard:</span> "Your file arrived yesterday. Standard protocol for new transfers."
</div>

Fair enough. Nothing sinister &mdash; just bureaucracy.

[[Take the elevator|DEMO-400 Office]]
<</page>>


:: DEMO-300 Street
<<silently>>
<<set $header.location to "City Centre &mdash; Street">>
<<emote-calm>>
<</silently>>
<<header>>
<<page>>

You walk along the street. A coffee shop on the corner catches your eye. The smell of fresh roast drifts through the open door.

A newsstand displays the morning headlines. Nothing interesting &mdash; just politics and weather.

<<addNotification "You explored the street.">>

[[Get coffee|DEMO-310 Coffee]]
[[Head to the building|DEMO-200 Lobby]]
<</page>>


:: DEMO-310 Coffee
<<silently>>
<<set $header.time to "Monday, 08:30">>
<</silently>>
<<header>>
<<page>>

You order a flat white and take it to go. The warmth in your hands is grounding.

<<set $player.statusEffects.pushUnique("Caffeinated")>>
<<addNotification "Status effect: Caffeinated">>

//Better get to work.//

[[Head to the building|DEMO-200 Lobby]]
<</page>>


:: DEMO-400 Office
<<silently>>
<<set $header.location to "Office &mdash; Third Floor">>
<<set $header.time to "Monday, 08:45">>
<<emote-calm>>
<</silently>>
<<header>>
<<page>>

The elevator opens onto a quiet floor. Cubicles line the walls, but only a few are occupied this early.

A woman with short dark hair waves you over from a corner office.

<div class="dialogue">
    <span class="speaker">Director Chen:</span> "<<playerFullName>>. Welcome aboard. We have a lot to discuss."
</div>

She gestures to a chair across from her desk.

//This is where it begins.//

<<addNotification "Prologue complete.">>

<div class="decisions">
    <a data-passage="Start">Return to Main Menu</a>
</div>
<</page>>
